I"c<h1 id="the-art-of-accountability">The art of accountability</h1>
<p>I had a manager that I would constantly butt heads with. He was military minded. I never seemed to have the right answer for him. I would explain to him endlessly. 
Truth be told, no one cared for him. All for the same reasons. Everyone said “He just doesn’t care to listen.”</p>
